    "The reliance on the Google Search API for accuracy improvements underscores the need for models that maintain high performance even in the absence of external data sources, particularly in contexts where internet access is restricted or non-existent.",
    "Reduction in Hallucinations: Ethical ConsiderationsThe significant reduction in hallucinations highlights the potential of API integration to mitigate one of the most pressing ethical concerns associated with LLMs: the generation of misleading or factually incorrect information.",
    "By leveraging realtime data, Llama 2 7b demonstrates an ability to produce more reliable outputs, crucial for applications where the integrity of information is paramount.",
